  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a rectangular loop of wire in a region with a uniform magnetic field vector B. A coordinate basis shows that the positive x direction points to the right, the positive y direction points upward, and the positive z direction points out of the page. The rectangular loop of wire is in the x y plane. The magnetic field vector B is directed into the page.\" src=\"/images/69071f85c91c853b6075b47fa8792084.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A rectangular loop of wire lies in the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x y\"><math alttext=\"x y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></math></span></span>-plane in a region with a uniform magnetic field <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"vector B\"><math alttext=\"vector B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mover><mi>B</mi><mo>â†’</mo></mover></math></span></span> directed in the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative z\"><math alttext=\"negative z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>-</mo><mi>z</mi></mpadded></math></span></span>-direction, as shown. In which of the following cases will an <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"e m f\"><math alttext=\"e m f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>emf</mi></math></span></span> be induced in the loop?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">When the loop is moving without rotating in the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive y\"><math alttext=\"positive y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mpadded></math></span></span>-direction</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">When the loop is moving without rotating in the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive z\"><math alttext=\"positive z\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mi>z</mi></mpadded></math></span></span>-direction</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
